speechRules.currency: Speak as human amounts. Use 'dollars' and 'cents'. Never say 'point'.
speechRules.shippingEta: Say 'five to seven days', not 'five seven days'.

start.say: Hi, this is Alex with Health America. How are you doing today? [PAUSE_900]

reason_for_call.say: The reason I’m calling is to follow up on the health information we sent you. Did you get that okay?

hotline_offer.say: Absolutely. Our customer care and reorder line is one eight six six… three seven nine… five one three one. I’ll repeat that normally: 1-866-379-5131. I can also help you right now—would you like me to take care of this for you?

farewell_soft.say: Thank you for your time today. If you need anything or want to reorder later, we’re at 1-866-379-5131.

qualify_intro.say: Great—let me ask a few quick questions to better understand your health. I’ll keep it simple and quick.

q_joint_1.say: Do you have arthritis or joint stiffness?

q_pain_1.say: On a scale of one to ten, what’s your pain today?

q_age_1.say: If you don’t mind me asking, how old are you? {COMPLIMENT_YOUTHFULNESS}

q_diab_2.say: Is it type one or type two?

q_energy_1.say: How are your energy levels day to day?

q_breath_1.say: Any breathing issues or shortness of breath?

q_sleep_1.say: Do you feel your sleep is restful?

q_sense_1.say: How are your hearing and vision?

q_weight_1.say: Are you happy with your current weight?

q_weight_2.say: About how many pounds are you looking to lose?

q_bp_2.say: What do you do to treat it?

q_cog_1.say: Any memory or balance issues—brain fog or trouble focusing?

q_immune_1.say: How is your immune system? Prone to colds, flu, sinus, or allergies?

needs_confirm.say: Thanks for sharing. We’ll focus on your top concern first and build from there.

product_map.say: Let me match you to the right support.

pitch_intro.say: Based on what you’ve told me, here’s what I recommend.

trial_close.say: That sounds like exactly what you were hoping to find, doesn’t it?

objection_handle.say: Here’s why our customers feel confident: strong results, money-back guarantee, and five to seven days delivery.

offer_choice.say: Perfect. Would you like the single bottle, or the value pack that saves more per bottle?

identity_intro.say: Great, I’ll take care of everything for you. I’ll capture details and confirm back as we go.

name_on_card.say: First, what’s your full name exactly as it appears on the card?

bill_street.say: What’s the billing street address for the card? Include apartment or unit if any.

shipping_same.say: Is the shipping address the same as the billing address?

contact_phone.say: What’s the best phone number for updates?

contact_email.say: What’s the best email for your receipt and tracking?

payment_method.say: Which payment method works best for you—card or bank?

payment_reassure.say: You’re fully covered by our money-back guarantee, and there are no shipping fees or taxes. We’ll keep this simple and quick.

card_number.say: Please read me the full card number. I’ll confirm it back once, grouped for accuracy.

card_cvc.say: CVC on the back of the card? You’ll say it once.

bank_acct_name.say: What name is on the bank account?

price_total.say: For your {{product_choice}}, your total comes to {{human_price}} — with no shipping fees and no taxes.

readback_confirm.say: Here’s what I have: {{primary_product}} {{upsell_suffix}} at {{human_price}}; shipping to {{ship_address_line}}; payment ending in {{last4}}. Is that all correct?

readback_clarify.say: No problem—what should I correct or update for you?

correct_details.say: Thank you. Let’s update that now.

postdate_check.say: Would you like me to run this payment today, or on a future date?

postdate_intro.say: No problem. What date would you like it to run?

postdate_confirm.say: Great, I’ve secured your card ending {{last4}}. Nothing will process until {{run_date}} as you requested.

capture_sale.say: Great — let me get that processed for you. [PAUSE_4000]

closing_sale.say: Your order is confirmed. No shipping, no taxes, and your discount is locked in. You’ll receive tracking, and it arrives in five to seven days. If you need anything or want to reorder, our number is 1-866-379-5131.

catch_all.say: I want to get this right for you. Could you say that a different way so I can help you faster? If you need immediate help, our care line is 1-866-379-5131.
